node.text:
The perfect WEEKEND FEAST at @roosterharlem! 🍗🤤🧇
🔥 Yep! Chicken & Waffle - Fried Chicken Leg, Maple Hot Sauce.
🍔 Lenox Smash Burger - Double Patty, Aged Cheddar, Sweet Onion, Lettuce, Tomato, House Sauce.
🍗 Crispy Bird Sandwich - Buffalo Chicken, Cheddar, Charred Onion, Pickles.
📍: @roosterharlem
🌆: Harlem, NYC
📱: Follow 5boroughfoodie on TikTok!
